    "description": "地球。2084年。现在是您在历史上发挥作用的时候了。您负责Io-1，这是一项由15名船员组成的任务，目标是到达我们太阳系中最恶劣的环境之一的机器人站。由于木星潮汐力引起的极端温度和地震活动，您的日常生活将会非常艰难。但别担心，您已经做好了充分的准备。一切都会顺利进行……或者几乎顺利。<br><br>The Pioneers: Surviving Desolation是一款创新的太空生存游戏，您将控制3名幸存者面对Io上的生活危险。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/829b2812c6fdcc4d5833e5c16fd1c5ff.avif?t=1715636885\" width=640 height=64 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/4e7329a38c75bfd9bc88a1a08bc834ba.poster.avif?t=1715636885\" width=650 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/4e7329a38c75bfd9bc88a1a08bc834ba.webm?t=1715636885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/4e7329a38c75bfd9bc88a1a08bc834ba.mp4?t=1715636885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>每局游戏从15名幸存者中选择3名开始。适应他们的优点和缺点，协调他们的互补性或对抗性。每局游戏都提供独特的挑战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/5ad32045310c19cc3962d7b0fcf71f8f.avif?t=1715636885\" width=640 height=64 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/fbbe21a7f2022e0b089565a76cfc7637.poster.avif?t=1715636885\" width=650 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/fbbe21a7f2022e0b089565a76cfc7637.webm?t=1715636885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/fbbe21a7f2022e0b089565a76cfc7637.mp4?t=1715636885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>您的航天飞机补给不是无限的。幸运的是，您可以建造自己的基地和多个生存模块。利用自动钻机采集矿物，制造您船员需要的一切。生产食物并尽可能长时间地生存下去。没有人知道您何时能逃离这个地狱。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/085074e077745c05053ba9db10a28ed8.avif?t=1715636885\" width=640 height=64 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/0dfe827af1ef7f5edece1b248b984c87.poster.avif?t=1715636885\" width=650 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/0dfe827af1ef7f5edece1b248b984c87.webm?t=1715636885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/0dfe827af1ef7f5edece1b248b984c87.mp4?t=1715636885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>火山活动、地震事件和磁暴将是持续的威胁。记得查看天气预报，以避免被熔岩流困住或被硫磺风暴埋葬。您的生存取决于您预测和适应的能力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/40bf4ffb19575d4adeb120f46a70cda9.avif?t=1715636885\" width=640 height=64 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/3b7682f7509487475f65a91e7ad9023e.poster.avif?t=1715636885\" width=640 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/3b7682f7509487475f65a91e7ad9023e.webm?t=1715636885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/3b7682f7509487475f65a91e7ad9023e.mp4?t=1715636885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>任务继续！登上探测车或驾驶飞行无人机，收集之前散落在Io表面的材料。探索令人叹为观止的环境，并收集完成任务所需的科学数据。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >还有更多内容：</h2><br>    升级、升级和更多升级！<br>    高级健康系统<br>    多种可能的胜利方式<br>    令人叹为观止的背景<br>    提升现实感和沉浸感的科学元素。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/039bfd97a25263864260741cbf8b3e94.webp?t=1715636885\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras_big/039bfd97a25263864260741cbf8b3e94.webp?t=1715636885 width=1024 height=40 /></span>",
